<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="air-n">air <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /eə(r)/    美 /er/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>空气；天空；空中：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>air conditioning / conditioners</strong>
空调系统/空调机</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Birds are flying high up <strong>in the air</strong>. 
鸟儿在高空中飞翔。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It saves a great deal of time to travel <strong>by air</strong>. 
乘飞机出行能节省很多时间。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>神态；样子：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The dog hardly ate anything and had such an <strong>air of</strong> sadness.
这条狗没怎么吃东西，一副很忧郁的样子。</p><footer>2010 北京改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-the-air">in the air</h3>
<p>1.<strong>(某种情绪) 弥漫在空气中；即将发生：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There was a sense of excitement in the air. 
到处洋溢着一种激动的气氛。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Change is in the air. 
变革迫在眉睫。</p></div>

<h3 id="on-off-the-air">on / off (the) air</h3>
<p>1.<strong>正在/停止广播：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We’ll be on air in three minutes. 
我们三分钟后开始广播。</p></div></div>